## Animation & Motion

### Subtle Motion Principles
- **Purposeful**: Every animation serves a functional purpose
- **Subtle**: No distracting or excessive motion
- **Performance**: 60fps target, respect reduced motion preferences
- **Accessibility**: Always provide reduced motion alternatives

### Framer Motion Patterns
```typescript
